<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>Upa Chunga</author>
<hymn_number>120</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Kalvari hinna thisan lui luong,
 Chapsuok menghen khawvel cheng leh gam hi;
 Nangmah tatsa lei mihingte,
 Thihna hansie kala leng ui.

[V2]
 Lalpa Isu Na lopina leh hehpihna,
 Taklang mengin namtin laiah;
 Mihing lung gitloh a liem san,
 Na min lambang pak zaila sau hen.

[V3]
 2. Ka gam uh lungngaih buoina kalah,
 Kuo a Lalpa, Hukdam dinga kuon ding;
 Sim leh Mal a Nangmah minlun,
 Panpihtu ding dang a um puoi.

[V4]
 3. Khawvel gitlohna meipi guol in,
 A hung zing ie Lalpa ka lungguk ah;
 Hun hal thieng in van mei kuongin,
 Nang di'n pak thing bang lun kit ka.

[V5]
 4. Ka kap Lalpa Na gam lun ngai in,
 Kum khawtuong gam leh lung lun Mang lenna;
 Bangtik phat leh lungkham mauna,
 Pela luonthi dai bang kan ding?</lyrics>
<title>Kalvari Hehpihna</title>
</song>